@startuml
' Visual Configuration
skinparam Style strictuml
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam MaxMessageSize 150

actor "Hospital Staff" as Staff #LightBlue
participant "Blood Platform\n(Server)" as System #White
database "Database" as DB #White
actor "Eligible Donor" as Donor #LightGreen

== Step 1: Emergency Request Creation ==

Staff -> System : Submit Emergency Request (Type, Quantity, Location) [cite: 108, 109]
activate System

System -> DB : Query compatible donors in 5-50km radius [cite: 93, 178]
activate DB
DB --> System : Return list of matched donors [cite: 94]
deactivate DB

== Step 2: Real-Time Notification ==

System -> System : Trigger Smart Matching Algorithm [cite: 48, 123]
note right : Target response: < 3 seconds 

System -> Donor : Send Push Notification (Urgency, Distance) [cite: 61, 177]
activate Donor

== Step 3: Donor Response ==

Donor -> System : Click "I Can Donate" [cite: 180, 201]
deactivate Donor

System -> DB : Increment "Committed Donor" count [cite: 201]
System -> Staff : Update Request Status: Donor Found [cite: 137]

== Step 4: System Auto-Management ==

alt Donor Commitments >= 150% of Required Units [cite: 198]
    System -> System : Change status to "Pending Fulfillment" [cite: 202]
    System -> DB : Stop broadcasting request [cite: 193, 203]
    System -> Staff : Notify: Goal Reached [cite: 202]
end

deactivate System

@enduml